                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-rating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">"Great quality products at affordable prices. I shop here regularly now."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-author">- Michael Chen</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-rating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">"The return process was so easy. This is how online shopping should be!"</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-author">- Emily Davis</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Secondary CTA Section -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cta-content">
                    <h2>Ready to Start Shopping?</h2>
                    <p>Join thousands of satisfied customers and discover amazing deals today.</p>
                    <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

